.SH EXAMPLES
.IX Header "EXAMPLES"
To see program arguments:
.PP
.Vb 1
\&    ciscodump \-\-help
.Ve
.PP
To see program version:
.PP
.Vb 1
\&    ciscodump \-\-version
.Ve
.PP
To see interfaces:
.PP
.Vb 1
\&    ciscodump \-\-extcap\-interfaces
.Ve
.PP
Only one interface (cisco) is supported.
.PP
.Vb 2
